# Dexie.js

> Minimalistic IndexedDB wrapper with a straightforward API for offline-first web applications.

---

## Overview

Dexie.js simplifies IndexedDB development:
- **Simple API**: Promise-based, intuitive syntax
- **Type-Safe**: Full TypeScript support
- **Reactive**: Built-in live queries
- **Offline-First**: Perfect for local-first architecture
- **Performant**: Efficient bulk operations

---

## Why Dexie

| vs Raw IndexedDB | vs LocalStorage | vs SQLite (WASM) |
|------------------|-----------------|------------------|
| 10x simpler API | Structured data | No WASM overhead |
| Promise-based | Larger storage | Native browser API |
| Transactions | Indexing support | Better compatibility |

